Package se.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Library
    Library API main class.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BookAlreadyBorrowedException
    Book unable to be borrowed because there is another user already set as borrower.
    BookNotFoundException
    Book of a given title was not found in the database.
    RequestNotFoundException
    Request with a given book title was not found in the database.
    TooManyBorrowsException
    User has already reached max. number of borrows specified in the system.
    UserNotFoundException
    User of a given name was not found in the database.
